scene.message:
Pandora: Why won't you{nl}
give up? All of you...{nl}
How can you be so strong?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: It's because we're{nl}
not "I" but "We"...{nl}
because we're not alone.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: It's because we're{nl}
not "I" but "We"...{nl}
because we're not alone.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...{nl}
No one can live alone.{nl}
When it hurts, look back -{waitkey}we'll always be there.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: You and I are both{nl}
part of the same{nl}
Maki Sonomura...{waitkey}a friend to everyone here.{nl}
Let's stop this - let's{nl}
try our best together.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Thank you all, truly.{nl}
This is goodbye, but...{nl}
I'll never forget you...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I'm a shadow of Maki{nl}
Sonomura. I can't go{nl}
with you all... It was{nl}
really fun, though...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey! Sonomura!{nl}
That's not fair!{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Whoa!!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Thank you...{nl}
Now and then, just{nl}
remember me, okay?{waitkey}Farewell... I love you...{waitkey}{ret}
